Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.27,0:06:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩網路遊戲必須和供應商簽約
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.10,0:06:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,取得帳號之後才可以玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那要到哪裡簽約？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說明書最後一頁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有供應商的電話號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先在畫面上連到那裡看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.46,0:06:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它說“因您的線路問題無法連線”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你現在正透過\N電話線路和我通電話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我一邊看說明書
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一邊想辦法試試看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.98,0:07:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要開始玩遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來還得花不少時間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個授權費是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.46,0:07:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個月要一千元？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，第一個月是免費的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寬頻接頭是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密碼錯誤？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看他睡得這麼正大光明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道該說什麼才好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密碼又錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.92,0:07:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是網路設定\N你自己搞定好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.86,0:07:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:08:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，就算看說明書我也不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（連線成功）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，連上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經連上線了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以跟秀樹一起玩遊戲嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.31,0:08:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該一開始就去找新保幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，那就馬上來開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.82,0:08:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說嘛，新保
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.59,0:08:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也來一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正想回去預習\N明天補習班要上的地方耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一天不預習沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下，休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來嘛，來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起玩，一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.74,0:08:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，要開始囉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.28,0:08:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，遊戲開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.52,0:08:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了，來了，來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳躍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.06,0:08:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劍是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個遊戲連表情都會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.03,0:09:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來就像是個菜鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個遊戲會隨著我們的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改變表情或動作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清…清水老師，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就關掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我啦，是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你的角色\N那麼像清水老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我臨時做出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是感覺上很像而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.78,0:09:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過那張臉\N配那個聲音總覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，讓我們去冒險吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為遊戲裡可以自由調整大小
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ不在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在哪裡？ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳到哪裡去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:09:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.85,0:09:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲進行時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:10:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他的機能都會停止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.98,0:10:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那ちぃ怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.39,0:10:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有ちぃ不在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.76,0:10:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是連到其他伺服器了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來你總算連上線了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.37,0:10:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這遊戲對於不同的城鎮\N會使用不同的伺服器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.40,0:10:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藉此限制同時上線的玩家人數
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個城鎮已經客滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ可能被強制傳送到\N其他城鎮去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.18,0:10:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得快去找她才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.99,0:10:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說的其他城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為通常有20個伺服器在運作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裡面又各分成15個城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合計共有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不管那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.26,0:10:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能讓ちぃ孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才說菜鳥真討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:10:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你這種人來玩的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲會變得很難玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你千萬不要做奇怪的事喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了，本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你一個人的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰都可以自由進來玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.96,0:11:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是一樣喜歡說漂亮話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.56,0:11:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國分寺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你認識我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.23,0:11:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你在網路上很有名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.83,0:11:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你那個菜鳥好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.91,0:11:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,網路上也有那種沒禮貌的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間在這裡閒聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等我喔，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.83,0:11:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.41,0:12:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.94,0:12:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.87,0:12:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就會找到妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以多欺少太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劍對那些傢伙是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要仔細閱讀說明書
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.51,0:12:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.68,0:12:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道這類的遊戲你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，我是第一次玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高中時因為老是在照顧牛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒時間玩遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣還敢一個人獨自冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.82,0:12:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太魯莽了，太笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.19,0:12:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你不要一個人去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.43,0:13:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有那麼多恐怖的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我更不能讓ちぃ孤單一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這只是遊戲而已耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而已耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要吃我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好燙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全一副菜鳥樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.54,0:13:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.94,0:13:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太魯莽了，太笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（存檔中）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（存檔完畢）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結…結果還是沒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲結束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.33,0:14:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳跑哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.77,0:14:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我聽到了秀樹的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是沒有跟秀樹在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，今天晚上再玩吧，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定能一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.87,0:14:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這兩人的膽子還真大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在哪裡？ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.21,0:14:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.81,0:14:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果今天上課又睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去\N我真的考得上學校嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.39,0:15:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樂意之至
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不好看啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個啦，DVD
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你好像沒睡飽的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是看到天亮啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒買片子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.64,0:15:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒看過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.07,0:15:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，這個拿回去看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.68,0:15:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長，這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的秘密收藏品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.62,0:15:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候還我都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.35,0:15:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 DVD 的片子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長，你借了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是動作片啦，動作片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.53,0:15:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我珍藏的動作片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:16:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ大概很期待玩遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.24,0:16:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定能一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.18,0:16:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.08,0:16:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是也不能天天玩遊戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然對不起ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要好好睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.46,0:16:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天開始要拼命讀書
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來，秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也來玩遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要跟秀樹一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.81,0:16:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們今天也在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起玩才有趣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我要跟ちぃ一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，遊戲開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼ちぃ今天還是不在？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:17:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伺服器應該沒那麼多人才對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是因為人數的關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.34,0:17:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又跑到其他的城鎮去了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說如果電腦的性能太強時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會給遊戲的伺服器\N帶來很大的負擔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時候會不能玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.95,0:17:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警告，警告
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常危險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要單獨行動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.86,0:17:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對，不是那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，看招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你不要亂用魔法的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等我，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.94,0:17:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大魔王終於登場了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.58,0:18:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是打不倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他那麼強嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.12,0:18:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看雜誌和網路上的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒看過有人打倒過他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警告，警告
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.59,0:18:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險，危險
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.09,0:18:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請立刻避難
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.93,0:18:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通過這裡就可以到下個城鎮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你是認真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別想不開了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是打不贏那傢伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.60,0:18:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她也許正在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:18:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿他沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.25,0:18:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carbonara
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chorizo
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.79,0:19:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經不行了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.91,0:19:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ち…ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.67,0:20:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是ちぃ嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（恭喜過關）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.73,0:20:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ…ちぃ在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.13,0:20:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快幫我倒帶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這又不是錄影帶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過剛剛那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好像真的是ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.84,0:21:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好厲害喔，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ打倒了大魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.02,0:21:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ什麼都不記得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.35,0:21:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.42,0:21:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失蹤的ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.93,0:21:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以另一個角色的身份出現
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.90,0:21:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打倒無敵的大魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道ちぃ擁有\N超越伺服器等級的性能嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.00,0:21:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.27,0:21:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的 CPU 就跟超級電腦同等級…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.91,0:21:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，不玩遊戲了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，因為已經破關了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.15,0:21:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,況且ちぃ要是又不見了\N我會很傷腦筋的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.96,0:21:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ沒辦法一起玩遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.93,0:21:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那下次再玩別的遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.30,0:21:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩不必連上網路的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.43,0:21:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.07,0:22:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有別的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.37,0:22:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個是店長的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.18,0:22:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起玩這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.38,0:22:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小…ちぃ，那不是遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.98,0:22:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.38,0:22:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我跟妳說…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.78,0:22:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.38,0:23:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重考生沒有暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.28,0:23:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了讀書讀書，還是讀書
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.18,0:23:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.82,0:23:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是海灘陽傘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.25,0:24:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,義大利是世界的陽傘
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.29,0:24:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.89,0:24:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是游泳圈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.02,0:24:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水中的物體
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.16,0:24:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會受到其所排開的水\N相同重量的浮力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.56,0:24:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.16,0:24:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.00,0:24:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿，船，喘，串
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.00,0:24:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.77,0:24:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.17,0:24:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼會在海邊啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.37,0:24:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits 下一回\N「ちぃ，去海邊」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.17,0:24:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.28,0:24:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快樂喔
